---
const deployedAt = new Date().toISOString();
---

<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width" />
    <title>Astro on AWS Lambda</title>
    <style>
      body {
        font-family: system-ui, sans-serif;
        max-width: 640px;
        margin: 2rem auto;
        padding: 0 1rem;
        color: #333;
      }
      h1 { color: #6d28d9; }
      code { background: #f3f4f6; padding: 0.2rem 0.4rem; border-radius: 4px; font-size: 0.9rem; }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <h1>Astro on AWS Lambda</h1>
    <p>This page is server-rendered by Astro running in AWS Lambda, with static assets served from CloudFront CDN.</p>
    <p>Server rendered at: <code>{deployedAt}</code></p>
    <p><a href="/api/hello">Try the API endpoint &rarr;</a></p>
  </body>
</html>
